item.title: Yercaud: A Trip With Older Generation
You Think Your Multitaskpro Think Again??
item.description: Hey you if you are here and reading this, know that you have definitely reached internets treasure trove. You ain’t getting any gold, but definitely something more - knowledge, entertainment, philosophy and good music to touch your soul can you put a price on that. Keep life simple while you rise and shine Well sometimes you navigate the web rightfully you end up on places that are quite exciting and definitely inspirational people with some pretty exciting talent.

item.title: Dude you broke the future
item.description: This is pretty cool talk by Charles Stross, given at Chaos Computer Club congression this talk reflects my opinion or views on current world of corporates, startups, artificial intelligence (referred by speaker as corporate AI and computerized AI) and one ridiculed CEO or lets say more than one [:P]. You can also find reason’s on why I quit facebook or hated it in the first place. The talk starts by saying on how prediction 3 centuries back or even a century back was possible to do accurately.
